# CUR-1557: build-context ignore scoped to the coverage-image build ONLY.
# BuildKit resolves `<dockerfile>.dockerignore` before the repo-root
# `.dockerignore`, so this does NOT affect the sponsor-ci / portal-final builds
# that rely on the repo-root context. The coverage Dockerfile only COPYs apps/,
# so exclude everything else -- most importantly .git (large with
# fetch-depth: 0), plus node_modules / build output -- to keep the context small.
*
!apps
